msgstr "మీ సర్వర్ URLని కనుగొనడం"

#. plugin:custom-links:section:3:content
#: 
msgid "For security:\n"
"- Only administrators can add or remove links\n"
"- The 'Manage Links' option only appears for administrators\n"
"- Links must use http:// or https:// protocols\n"
"- HTML tags are not allowed in names or URLs\n"
